    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1 H3C LA2608 室内无线网关用户手册",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            61,
            610,
            84
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.1 概述",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            102,
            194,
            122
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608需要通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            138,
            905,
            174
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/0e2eb77b873265be02b023ce2afe6cf44de34b831f737f62b241d4317d028886.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            188,
            184,
            212
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "bbox": [
            188,
            198,
            223,
            212
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目前，LA2608只支持与 H3C公司的无线控制器互通。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            224,
            561,
            239
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            282,
            482,
            302
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            320,
            905,
            355
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/f204a8881b1075be8d2d10c4dc2e261e7f3bcf139057a7bd2350d558b8ea6198.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "图1 配置 LA2608与无线控制器互通"
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    A[\"Host A\"] -->|WIFI| B[\"LA2608\"]\n    C[\"Host B\"] -->|WIFI| B\n    D[\"Host C\"] -->|WIFI| B\n    B -->|3G/4G| E[\"Internet\"]\n    E --> F[\"AC\"]\n```",
        "sub_type": "flowchart",
        "bbox": [
            147,
            391,
            808,
            584
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.1 配置LA2608",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            625,
            260,
            642
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            659,
            438,
            675
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n<LA2608>system-view \n```",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            684,
            310,
            695
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            700,
            413,
            712
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2) 配置 DCC 拨号",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            716,
            305,
            732
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/e381047ffd55b50c2649968ebbf1e1fb8204f864fcbd8adbaa7c23aafd4126f5.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            747,
            186,
            770
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "bbox": [
            188,
            756,
            225,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            781,
            904,
            815
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```powershell\n[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0 \n```",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            850,
            645,
            929
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            505,
            948,
            514,
            958
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number *99# autodial\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            51,
            626,
            114
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            117,
            342,
            133
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[LA2608]dns resolve \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            141,
            310,
            153
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4) 配置静态路由",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            157,
            295,
            173
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0 \n```",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            181,
            660,
            194
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP 地址",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            197,
            445,
            213
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143 \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            220,
            430,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            248,
            352,
            264
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8595b5e0431211ff1fcc244ac1d195c418463eea29d726b873ccc03e27578124.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            290,
            186,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            188,
            298,
            225,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如下配置仅供参考，运营商可根据实际情况进行调整。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            324,
            559,
            339
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            374,
            312,
            389
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n<AC>system-view\n[AC]vlan 2\n[AC-vlan2] quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            397,
            277,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2) 创建 WLAN-ESS 接口并加入业务 VLAN",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            447,
            500,
            461
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[AC]interface WLAN-ESS 1\n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]port access vlan 2\n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            471,
            421,
            516
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3) 配置明文方式的服务模板",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            521,
            384,
            536
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[AC]wlan service-template 1 clear\n[AC-wlan-st-1]ssid ssidh3c\n[AC-wlan-st-1]bind WLAN-ESS 1\n[AC-wlan-st-1]service-template enable\nPlease wait... Done.\n[AC-wlan-st-1]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            543,
            465,
            638
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4) 开启自动 AP 功能",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            644,
            329,
            659
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[AC]wlan auto-ap enable\n[AC]wlan ap 2608 model LA2608 id 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]serial-id auto\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]radio 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]service-template 1\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]radio enable\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]quit\n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            667,
            515,
            796
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5) 配置 VLAN 接口 IP 地址",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            800,
            376,
            815
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```ini\n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1\n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0\n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit\n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2\n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0\n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            824,
            635,
            919
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(6) 使能 DHCP 服务，配置 DHCP 地址池 ",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            923,
            482,
            939
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            505,
            948,
            515,
            959
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n[AC]dhcp enable\n[AC]dhcp server ip-pool vlan2\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]network 10.249.136.0 22\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]gateway-list 10.249.136.1\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]dns-list 218.201.96.130\n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]quit \n```",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            51,
            532,
            148
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.3 验证LA2608 与无线控制器是否连通",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            162,
            468,
            180
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在无线控制器上执行 display wlan ap 命令，state 字段显示为“R/M”，表示 LA2608 与无线控制器之间已经建立连接。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            195,
            907,
            229
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "```txt\n<Sysname> display wlan ap all\nTotal Number of APs configured : 1\nTotal Number of configured APs connected : 1\nTotal Number of auto APs connected : 0\nAP Profiles\nState : I = Idle, J = Join, JA = JoinAck, IL = ImageLoad\nC = Config, R = Run, KU = KeyUpdate, KC = KeyCfm\nM = Master, B = Backup \n```",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            237,
            670,
            366
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "table",
        "img_path": "images/e5ccd12f9b861c241aff6b8085e298f8dd714129f42bd111f759cfa6055cb54e.jpg",
        "table_caption": [],
        "table_footnote": [],
        "table_body": "<table><tr><td>AP Name</td><td>State Model</td><td>Serial-ID</td></tr><tr><td>ap1</td><td>R/M LA2608</td><td>036286A054000033</td></tr></table>",
        "bbox": [
